Epic views hiking with @sophielovesasia 😍 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on explorerfervor.com (link in my bio: @explorerfervor) 

At the Yandang Mountains, picturesque coastal mountain range with sharp rock peaks, waterfalls & verdant forest.

Located in the southeastern China's Zhejiang province, this Via Ferrata combines a gorgeous scenery & thrilling adventures!

Would you dare to do it? Tag someone who would!

📽️ @sophielovesasia
📍Yandang Mountain, Zhejiang, China

node.text:
Umbrella tree 🌳 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting explorerfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @explorerfervor 

How impressive is this holm oak? Known as the umbrella tree. Once a year two gardeners climb up into its crown on ladders, and for two weeks they prune the tree like a skirt as they meticulously trim it into shape. Its healing powers helped James Bond recuperate – Casino Royale.

📽 @brigrc
📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy

This purring cheeta is the sweetest thing in the wild @nature 🐆We can post your pictures in our account. Check the link in our bio for more info: @explorerfervor 

Tag someone you’d like to cuddle like this 👇

📹 @wildcatcentre
